name: Perspectum
description:
An Interactive Piece by @Twistie42.
Made in p5.js on November 2, 2021.

Keybindings:
SPACEBAR -> SHUFFLE COLORS
RIGHT-ARROW -> INCREASE SPEED
LEFT-ARROW -> DECREASE SPEED
UP-ARROW -> INCREASE STROKE WEIGHT
DOWN-ARROW -> DECREASE STROKE WEIGHT
COMMA(,) -> DECREASE ALPHA
POINT(.) -> INCREASE ALPHA
